Insider Activity


Individual




Mirian M. Graddick-Weir



Dr. Mirian M. Graddick-Weir is Independent Director at Yum! Brands, Inc., Executive Vice President-Human Resources at Merck & Co., Inc., and Chairman at HR Policy Association. He is on the Board of Directors at Yum! Brands, Inc.
Dr. Graddick-Weir was previously employed as Executive Vice President-Human Resources by Merck Sharp & Dohme Corp., Executive Vice President-Human Resources by Schering-Plough Corp., Independent Director by Harleysville Group, Inc., and EVP-Human Resources & Employee Communications by AT&T Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from Hampton University, a graduate degree from Pennsylvania State University, and a doctorate degree from Pennsylvania State University.



